# Plan File Storage

Always save plan files to the **project-level** plans directory:

```
.cursor/plans/<plan-name>.plan.md
```

Do NOT save plans to `C:\Users\*\.cursor\plans\` (user home).

After `CreatePlan` runs (which defaults to the home directory), immediately move the file into the workspace `.cursor/plans/` folder using the Shell tool.
